he also rowed out twice to the island in the river , and made a sketch of the singular angles described by the rows of grey standing stones whose origin was so obscure and immemorial .
gilman room was of good size but queerly irregular shape ; the north wall slanting perceptibly inward from the outer to the inner end , while the low ceiling slanted gently downward in the same direction .
