about a heavy rumble was heard on the great bridge , followed by the sound of a coach in the street outside ; and at that hour there was no need of waiting for weeden in order to know that the doomed man had set out for his last night of unhallowed wizardry .
a moment later , as the receding coach clattered faintly over the muddy dock bridge , weeden appeared ; and the raiders fell silently into military order in the street , shouldering the firelocks , , or whaling harpoons which they had with them .
