whatever the contents may have been after more than a century of burial , all was gone except a few slivers of decayed wood .
there were no wheel tracks , but the police have measured a single set of footprints which they found in the vicinity , and which indicate the boots of a man of refinement .
hart is inclined to link this incident with the digging discovered last march , when a party in a motor truck were frightened away after making a deep excavation ; but sergt .
